data.description: A Rare find in The Dairy! This home is a must see! Better than new! Charming full brick home with 9' ceilings and an open floor plan. A Place to call Home! One owner home !4 Spacious Bedrooms and 2 1/2 Baths! Master bathroom has separate shower with Garden tub, double vanity and a walk in closet,. Kitchen is built for the Chef of the Family! The privacy fence and covered back patio makes this perfect for entertaining , Family and Friends on a cool Fall evening! Home is conveniently located near Ditto Landing, Aldridge Creek Greenway, shops, and restaurants. The amenities are clubhouse and pool. Call for your showing today! This one won't last long!
